The wife and father of Mahir Khalid Rizik, the suicide terrorist who blew himself at DusitD2 hotel on Tuesday, have been arrested. A police source told the Star the two are being flown to Nairobi by officers from the Anti-Terror Police Unit for interrogations. The wife, Sahaila Mwinyi, was nabbed at Bakarani, Kisauni. The father whose identity is yet to be established was arrested at Majengo, Mvita.  More to follow...